          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h1>New Arrivals - Clothing for Women & Men Canada</h1>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_wFNpLM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Discover the freshest clothing for women and men in Canada at Plenty, where new arrivals are always on trend. Our collection is packed with the latest styles of clothing, shoes and accessories, perfect for every occasion—from everyday casual to chic work attire that can go from day to night. Freshen up your look this season with accessories such as our <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/collections/new-arrivals-womens\">newly arrived handbags</a> for women. There are also plenty of options for men to update their closets, including <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/collections/new-arrivals-mens?page=2\">new styles of jackets and jeans</a>. Shop our new arrivals today online or in-stores in Canada.</p>"
          }
        }
